      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To amend title 23, United States Code, with respect to funding the recreational trails program, to require a study to determine the best available estimate of the total amount of nonhighway recreational fuel taxes received by the Secretary of the Treasury, and for other purposes.</title>
